      <p><strong>JobCopilot:</strong> Browse aggregated jobs from multiple sources, use career tools (CV builder, cover letters, interview prep), optionally train AI for auto-apply (premium only). More fragmented experience across tools.</p>

      <h3>Automation vs Manual Effort</h3>
      <p><strong>Jobsolv:</strong> AI tailors resumes automatically. You review each one (30-60 seconds) before applying. No training required—works immediately.</p>
      <p><strong>JobCopilot:</strong> Free tier requires manual browsing (limited to 3 times per week). Auto-apply requires training the AI assistant first, which takes significant time. Premium plans unlock automation.</p>

