      <p><strong>Jobsolv:</strong> Each resume is tailored to match specific job requirements with ATS optimization. Higher interview rates because applications are precisely targeted.</p>
      <p><strong>JobCopilot:</strong> CV builder improves existing resumes but doesn't tailor per job. Auto-apply quality depends on how well you train the AI, which varies significantly.</p>

      <h3>Learning Curve</h3>
      <p><strong>Jobsolv:</strong> Simple setup—create profile, upload resume, start browsing. No training required. First tailored resume ready in 30-60 seconds.</p>
      <p><strong>JobCopilot:</strong> Requires training the AI assistant for best results. Free tier is limited. More complex setup process, especially for auto-apply features.</p>

